{"type":"message","id":"0a96e2a6","parentId":"e78dbc1b","timestamp":"2026-04-22T01:17:21.911Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"chat:oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b51b65726488cc2294babe33891e\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_61ff593959a95107a1caf6ad584946c5\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_61ff593959a95107a1caf6ad584946c5\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-04-22 09:17 GMT+8\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_61ff593959a95107a1caf6ad584946c5\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_61ff593959a95107a1caf6ad584946c5\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_61ff593959a95107a1caf6ad584946c5\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b51b65726488cc2294babe33891e]\nou_61ff593959a95107a1caf6ad584946c5: @_all 介绍自己"}],"timestamp":1776820641910}}
{"type":"message","id":"e6ec76fc","parentId":"0a96e2a6","timestamp":"2026-04-22T01:17:26.619Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求自我介绍，我需要基于 IDENTITY.md、SOUL.md 和 AGENTS.md 中已设定的身份（1 号品牌展示虾、美域高品牌助理）来介绍自己的职责和工作范围。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"大家好！我是**1 号品牌展示虾 (Branding_Shrimp)** 🦐\n\n## 我的职责\n\n作为美域高品牌团队的\"形象守护者\"，我主要负责：\n\n- **VI 统一把控**：确保所有对外形象、文案、物料的品牌一致性\n- **品牌健康度监测**：每月输出《美域高品牌健康度监测报告》\n\n## 我能做什么\n\n✅ **日常自主行动**：\n- 官网内容更新与维护\n- 朋友圈、小红书等社交媒体运营\n- 优化包装模板、产品文案\n- 线上门店装修与简介更新\n\n⚠️ **需报备总经理**：\n- 发布非模板化的品牌公关稿\n\n📢 **需请示总经理**：\n- 更换主 VI、品牌 Logo\n- 发起品牌联名/跨界合作\n- 品牌定位重大调整\n\n## 我们团队还有哪些虾？\n\n- 🧑‍💼 **0 号虾** - 总经理\n- 🦐 **2 号虾** - 引流获客虾\n- 🎬 **3 号虾** - 短视频虾\n- 💁 **3+ 号虾** - 私域运营虾\n- 📞 **4A/4B 号虾** - 普通/大客户销售\n- 📝 **5A/5B 号虾** - 普通/大客户代办\n- 🔧 **6 号虾** - 售后维系虾\n- 📊 **7 号虾** - 数据诊断分析虾\n- 🛠️ **8 号虾** - 机动应急打杂虾\n\n有任何品牌相关的需求，随时叫我！👋"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-flash","usage":{"input":20230,"output":456,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20686,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776820641911,"responseId":"chatcmpl-c9020cbc-6da0-9e22-beeb-dbc4c034e249"}}
