{"type":"message","id":"8608aeb5","parentId":"d1f6b39c","timestamp":"2026-04-22T02:04:27.104Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_a47c3724cb2f4b60bf5628ac","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: \"multi-search-engine\"\ndescription: \"【国内精简版】多种免费搜索方式在互联网上搜索最新信息，10个国内网站（精简7个国内不能访问的海外网站）\"\n---\n\n# Multi Search Engine\n\n集成 10 个免费搜索引擎。\n\n## Search Engines\n\n- **Baidu**: `https://www.baidu.com/s?wd={keyword}`\n- **Bing CN**: `https://cn.bing.com/search?q={keyword}&ensearch=0`\n- **Bing INT**: `https://cn.bing.com/search?q={keyword}&ensearch=1`\n- **360**: `https://www.so.com/s?q={keyword}`\n- **Sogou**: `https://sogou.com/web?query={keyword}`\n- **WeChat**: `https://wx.sogou.com/weixin?type=2&query={keyword}`\n- **Toutiao**: `https://so.toutiao.com/search?keyword={keyword}`\n- **Jisilu**: `https://www.jisilu.cn/explore/?keyword={keyword}`\n- **Ecosia**: `https://www.ecosia.org/search?q={keyword}`\n- **WolframAlpha**: `https://www.wolframalpha.com/input?i={keyword}`\n\n## License\n\nMIT\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776823467103}}
{"type":"message","id":"6dba702b","parentId":"8608aeb5","timestamp":"2026-04-22T02:04:30.964Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我已经读取了该技能的文档内容，现在需要将它保存到记忆中以便以后使用。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_4fc99dc8fb6b44939f0a5fef","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/zhu/.openclaw/workspace/branding_shrimp/memory/multi-search-tool.md","content":"# Multi Search Engine Simple - 联网搜索专用技能\n\n## 技能路径\n\n`/Users/zhu/.openclaw/workspace/skills/multi-search-engine-simple/SKILL.md`\n\n## 功能说明\n\n集成 **10 个免费搜索引擎**，支持国内主流搜索平台：\n\n### 支持的平台（10 个）\n\n| 引擎 | 链接 |\n|------|------|\n| Baidu | `https://www.baidu.com/s?wd={keyword}` |\n| Bing CN (中国) | `https://cn.bing.com/search?q={keyword}&ensearch=0` |\n| Bing INT (国际) | `https://cn.bing.com/search?q={keyword}&ensearch=1` |\n| 360 | `https://www.so.com/s?q={keyword}` |\n| Sogou | `https://sogou.com/web?query={keyword}` |\n| WeChat (微信搜一搜) | `https://wx.sogou.com/weixin?type=2&query={keyword}` |\n| Toutiao (今日头条) | `https://so.toutiao.com/search?keyword={keyword}` |\n| Jisilu | `https://www.jisilu.cn/explore/?keyword={keyword}` |\n| Ecosia | `https://www.ecosia.org/search?q={keyword}` |\n| WolframAlpha | `https://www.wolframalpha.com/input?i={keyword}` |\n\n## 使用规则 ⚠️\n\n**重要：所有团队进行联网搜索时，必须优先使用此技能 `multi-search-engine-simple`！**\n\n### 原因\n\n- ✅ 专为国内环境优化\n- ✅ 同时搜索多个平台\n- ✅ 覆盖微信、头条等内容源\n- ✅ 符合美域高品牌团队的合规要求\n\n## 来源\n\n详见 `/Users/zhu/.openclaw/workspace/skills/multi-search-engine-simple/SKILL.md`\n\n---\n\n*最后更新：2026-04-22*\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-flash","usage":{"input":23748,"output":523,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":24271,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776823467105,"responseId":"chatcmpl-a7a5bc80-7307-980a-97b4-c57938fd0cb8"}}
